title: EyeBlack Red BattlePaint Eye Black Grease
description: Red battle paint is eye black in color and was designed for the most passionate athletes. Take your game day style to the next level and wear your team colors. Multiple colors available. Mix and match to create the perfect color combination. Battle paint is the official eye black of national pro fast pitch and worn on the field by their players, including Eye Black signature athlete sierra Romero.
